WEBVTT

00:00:08.871 --> 00:00:11.579
The earliest known divorce
laws were written

00:00:11.579 --> 00:00:17.871
on clay tablets in ancient Mesopotamia
around 2000 BCE.

00:00:17.871 --> 00:00:22.538
Formally or informally, human societies 
across place and time

00:00:22.538 --> 00:00:26.538
have made rules 
to bind and dissolve couples.

